725621f-a.title: Queens: 73rd Avenue - 182nd Street
725621f-a.text:
73rd Avenue, south side, at 182nd Street, showing an old farmhouse, at one time a tenant house of the Skidmores. The ownership of thia dwelling in 1873 is indicated by the initials J. D. Jacob Schleider owned it from 1891 to 1909. It
was then on a 46-acre farm.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  1922
